# Host-specific override for the watchdog systemd unit only.
#
# watchdog runs as a host systemd service (not Docker Compose), so it can't
# resolve the compose-network "redis" hostname used by /opt/alphadivision/.env.
# Redis is published to the host on 127.0.0.1:6379 (see docker-compose.yml).
#
# systemd applies EnvironmentFile= entries in the order they're listed, with
# later files overriding earlier ones for the same key — and EnvironmentFile=
# always overrides a plain Environment= directive regardless of ordering. So
# this file must be loaded via a second EnvironmentFile= line AFTER
# /opt/alphadivision/.env in watchdog.service to take effect.
#
# Not a secret — safe to commit.
REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379
